BRAUDLE
AI-Powered Personal Learning Platform

Full Product & Technical Documentation
Version 1.0  |  Stack: Next.js (TS) · Node.js (JS) · Express · MongoDB · Docker

Author: Abraham (Jide)  |  May 2026

WHAT IS BRAUDLE?	BRAUDLE is an AI-powered personal tutor web app that transforms uploaded study materials (PDFs, notes) into interactive, adaptive learning experiences. It teaches, questions, evaluates, and personalises lessons for every student — acting as a 24/7 private tutor.

MVP SCOPE	User signup/login  |  PDF upload (2/day)  |  Image notes upload (5/day)  |  AI Mode Selection  |  Quiz generation  |  Session summary with progress tracking
 
