User uploads file → Rate limit passes → Multer saves file to S3
↓
Document created in MongoDB (status: 'pending') → Job added to BullMQ queue
↓  API immediately returns documentId to frontend
Background Worker picks up job → Extraction (pdf-parse / Groq Vision)
↓
Semantic chunker splits text → Chunks stored in MongoDB
↓
Document status updated → 'ready' → Frontend prompts for session mode

↓
Semantic chunker splits text → Chunks stored in MongoDB
↓
Document status updated → 'ready' → Frontend polls and unlocks study session

